{"tid":1724350,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[突發] 蕭若元 : 勇武派需立即休息 ! !  咪再次中政府圈套 ! !  以免區議會選舉被取消 ! !","createTime":"2019-11-15T12:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T08:32:37.000Z","uid":219007,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5f7be70bb0b7db44a21d84e5bcc296b359ec3fc6","tid":1724350,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:32:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VLkDDaUOVd4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVLkDDaUOVd4&d=NKgE6Majit0rEYuBm%2F0CvlznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=b8775aa2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VLkDDaUOVd4</a><br />\n<br />\n對於中大同學讓出吐露港感到十分欣慰,因為政府的策略好明顯任由示威者行動 , 企圖令民意逆轉<br />\n目的是藉此取消區議會選舉!<br />\n<br />\n香港政府每次都用呢啲方法,製造一啲好醜陋嘅畫面,令到香港市民唔再支持勇武派 , but勇武派永遠都上當 , 例如612警方防線特登撤退讓勇武派衝擊 , 71擺空城計 , 今次都唔例外!!!<br />\n佢每次擺低嘅利誘勇武派永遠都上當.只不過係政府每次都露出馬腳被人影到,奸有奸輸先搞到今日咁<br />\n<br />\n為了拆解呢個陰謀 , 建議將所有行動轉為象徵式行動 , 再比限期特區政府直至完成區議會選舉 ,  讓到區議會選舉成為全民投票是否支持成立獨立調查委員會!"},{"pid":"4bb185e6a9265e67252921ad81f35ec0d4448ef4","tid":1724350,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:32:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044e3e155c4e4bbfea021bd89349dce2ae0f69dd","tid":1724350,"uid":126606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:33:29.000Z","msg":"收撚皮啦燒若元！"},{"pid":"e1f696c67cf13e93e2020249f756d9be4e16fe64","tid":1724350,"uid":182984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:34:17.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e8b04dccd8fbc22cbefcbe8b444e1ed0b769a6","tid":1724350,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:35:00.000Z","msg":"又休息 仆街死啦"},{"pid":"1b352c50605c6cdc73f11a2d212f4f2d79ed9e38","tid":1724350,"uid":318037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:3